                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "Good morning everyone, I'm trying to test my first strategy with fixed stakes, and I would like to add an exposure control so that the maximum amount I bet into any selection is, for example, 5 EUR.\n\nFor back bets, I believe this would be equivalent to limiting the max exposure of the selection to 5, but for lay bets its a bit trickier since it the exposure depends on the odds.\n\nSince I would like this control to happen in the same place for both back\/lay bets, is the best way to go about this to just implement an instance of TradingControl that specifically handles this \"max bet stakes\"? This could be as simple as just allowing to bet once per selection_id, with fixed stakes."
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        ]
